  <ul>
    <li><a href="/tenant-shard-db/docs/admin/tenants">Tenants &amp; Users</a> &mdash; the membership layer these operations sit on top of</li>
    <li><a href="/tenant-shard-db/docs/admin/auth">Authentication</a> &mdash; how the calling admin proves who they are</li>
    <li><a href="/tenant-shard-db/docs/acl/overview">Access Control</a> &mdash; the ACL model that <code>transfer_ownership</code>, <code>delegate_access</code>, and <code>revoke_all_user_access</code> manipulate</li>
    <li><a href="/tenant-shard-db/docs/compliance/gdpr">GDPR</a> &mdash; right-to-erasure, which is the heavier sibling of <code>revoke_all_user_access</code></li>
  </ul>
</DocsLayout>
